Class AttackStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.security_manager.attack.AttackStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class AttackStep
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<AttackStep>
    Step in the attack tree for obtaining the goal. An attack step can have a type, a description, a probability, a cost, and an impact.
    Author:
    jakebackhouse
